short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Load all background tabs immediately when Chrome starts, so you don't have to wait when you switch to them.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
When Chrome starts, sometimes it doesn't load all your background tabs right away. Then when you switch to those tabs, you have to wait for them to load. 

If you don't want to wait, install this extension. All your tabs will be loaded immediately when Chrome starts and they will appear instantly when you switch to them.
